@Orders_TW_HostAddress = http://localhost:5221
@token = 

### ==================== AUTENTICACIÓN ====================
### Login - Obtener token JWT
# @name login
POST {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin"
}

###

### ==================== PRODUCTOS ====================
### Obtener productos paginados (por defecto: página 1, 10 items)
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products
Accept: application/json

###

### Obtener productos - página 2, 5 items por página
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products?page=2&pageSize=5
Accept: application/json

###

### Obtener TODOS los productos sin paginación
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products/all
Accept: application/json

###

### Obtener un producto por ID (ejemplo: ID = 1)
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear un nuevo producto (requiere autenticación)
POST {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto de prueba",
  "description": "Descripción del producto",
  "price": 99.99,
  "stock": 10
}

###

### Actualizar un producto (requiere autenticación)
PUT {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Producto actualizado",
  "description": "Nueva descripción",
  "price": 149.99,
  "stock": 20
}

###

### Eliminar un producto (requiere autenticación)
DELETE {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ==================== CLIENTES ====================
### Obtener todos los clientes
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear un nuevo cliente
POST {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "fullName": "Juan Pérez",
  "email": "juan.perez@example.com"
}

###

### ==================== ÓRDENES ====================
### Obtener todas las órdenes
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Obtener una orden específica por ID
GET {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/orders/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Crear una nueva orden
POST {{Orders_TW_HostAddress}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "customerId": 1,
  "orderItems": [
    {
      "productId": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    },
    {
      "productId": 2,
      "quantity": 1
    }
  ]
}

###

